1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,620 --> 00:00:55,540
=Episode 5=

3
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:02,640
Still don't know who I am?

4
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,680
I thought

5
00:01:05,159 --> 00:01:07,079
even the worst villain

6
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:09,239
would still have some memory

7
00:01:09,239 --> 00:01:10,560
of the evil they've done.

8
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:12,760
Who exactly are you?

9
00:01:13,359 --> 00:01:14,480
You've harmed too many people

10
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,040
to remember them all?

11
00:01:19,519 --> 00:01:21,920
Eight years ago,
that winter on Hou Mountain,

12
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:23,799
a boy covered in blood.

13
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:27,319
You're the one who branded me

14
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:29,519
with that searing iron
and left this mark.

15
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:33,640
Now that you did this,

16
00:01:34,799 --> 00:01:36,760
you should have known that one day,

17
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:38,799
karma would catch up.

18
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,359
What do you want?

19
00:01:41,719 --> 00:01:44,239
If you're going to kill me, then do it!

20
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:53,000
I spent eight years
as a hostage prince in Xiling,

21
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:55,480
bearing unspeakable pain,

22
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,480
before I barely escaped with my life.

23
00:01:58,319 --> 00:02:00,359
So why would I grant you
such an easy end?

24
00:02:01,319 --> 00:02:02,920
I want you, for the rest of your life,

25
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:08,719
to suffer a fate worse than death.

26
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:11,960
You wretched slave!

27
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,719
While you were busy choosing a husband
to break the curse,

28
00:02:14,159 --> 00:02:15,879
you never knew
that I was roaming the palace,

29
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,759
building a web of informants.

30
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:18,680
You wretched slave!

31
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,879
I've been waiting for this moment!

32
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,439
Mother!

33
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:25,759
Mother!

34
00:02:26,639 --> 00:02:27,319
Ruyi...

35
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,560
You filthy wretch!

36
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:36,599
Let go of Ruyi!

37
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:42,280
A needle piercing a jade-like finger...

38
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:45,039
Would that break

39
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,719
Mu Ruyi's heart?

40
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:49,240
Let my mother go!

41
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,639
She is innocent!

42
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,759
Innocent?

43
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,680
Xiling has done too much evil!

44
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:57,400
Everyone's handa are stained!

45
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:01,719
No one is innocent.

46
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,680
I'll kill you!

47
00:03:03,759 --> 00:03:05,000
You wretch!

48
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:06,039
You animal!

49
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,960
Let my mother go!

50
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:12,400
I'll kill you!

51
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:13,879
I'll kill you!

52
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:15,400
Let my mother go!

53
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,800
It seems Your Majesty

54
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:21,360
can still be of some use.

55
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,039
The blood from her fingers

56
00:03:27,159 --> 00:03:31,800
could make a painting
of winter plum blossoms.

57
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,360
I'll kill you!

58
00:03:33,639 --> 00:03:35,479
I'll kill you! Ling Xiao!

59
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:38,280
I'll kill you!

60
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:46,039
(Tablet of Mu Ruyi)
Mu Ruyi,

61
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,280
(Tablet of Mu Ruyi)
your ancestral tablet

62
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,479
has been prepared.

63
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,840
Ling Xiao,

64
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:53,800
I'll rip you apart!

65
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,400
I will find you and destroy you
even after death!

66
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,479
You'll rot in hell!

67
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,159
Fine.

68
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:04,000
We'll see who meets their end first.

69
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:09,360
Being treated like a pet,

70
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:10,759
I took it.

71
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:13,159
Being played like a puppet,

72
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:14,120
I took it.

73
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,480
Being humiliated in every possible way,

74
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:17,560
I also took it.

75
00:04:17,759 --> 00:04:19,000
I took so much,

76
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:21,199
all for this day

77
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:23,319
to kill you with my own hands.

78
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:41,279
Don't you enjoy the power
of being a princess?

79
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,480
Don't you enjoy

80
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,720
the feeling of everyone groveling
before you?

81
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:48,279
I want you to experience
what it feels like to be "graced".

82
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:50,079
Ling Xiao!

83
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,639
Stop!

84
00:04:52,839 --> 00:04:53,639
Stop!

85
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:55,600
You scumbag!

86
00:04:56,279 --> 00:04:57,439
Stop it!

87
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:01,519
Let your ancestors watch

88
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,399
how the noble Princess of Xiling

89
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,920
yields herself to me.

90
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,240
Back then,

91
00:05:07,759 --> 00:05:09,879
this is how you treated me.

92
00:05:15,060 --> 00:05:19,540
(Ancestral Tablets)

93
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,160
Mother.

94
00:05:57,879 --> 00:05:58,600
Mother.

95
00:06:09,639 --> 00:06:11,240
Why don't you just kill me?

96
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,560
Don't even think about it.

97
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,079
If you die,

98
00:06:18,319 --> 00:06:20,240
I will kill everyone

99
00:06:20,759 --> 00:06:22,399
and bury them with you.

100
00:06:27,079 --> 00:06:27,720
(Your Highness.)

101
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,680
(From the moment I met you,)

102
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:32,279
(everything seems
to have been destined.)

103
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,120
(Though you sit in a high place)

104
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,560
(and I am but a lowly servant,)

105
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,360
(we can't escape the pain
of losing love ones)

106
00:06:40,439 --> 00:06:41,720
(and the longing for our fathers.)

107
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,759
(It's the same for both of us.)

108
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:47,680
(The trust we once had between us.)

109
00:06:48,759 --> 00:06:50,040
(Every moment we shared,)

110
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:54,079
(hearts true, lives given.)

111
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,639
(They turned out to be)

112
00:06:57,720 --> 00:07:00,279
(nothing but your schemes.)

113
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:08,759
(You will pay with your blood.)

114
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:15,000
You're awake.

115
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:25,519
What are you afraid of?

116
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:27,560
Are you afraid of me?

117
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:29,240
You scumbag!

118
00:07:30,399 --> 00:07:31,560
What do you want now?

119
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:32,959
I'm not afraid of you.

120
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,439
Your Highness,

121
00:07:36,279 --> 00:07:38,160
you are as arrogant as ever.

122
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,959
You schemed,

123
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:44,839
you plotted,

124
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,959
you used every dirty trick.

125
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,600
Even so,

126
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:52,000
you are still of lowly birth,

127
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,639
so despicable.

128
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:00,680
Does it hurt?

129
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,959
Or does your heart hurt more?

130
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,040
Ridiculous.

131
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,879
When I look at you,

132
00:08:09,519 --> 00:08:11,040
I feel nothing

133
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,720
but disgust.

134
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:17,120
Your tongue may be sharp,

135
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,560
but this tells the truth.

136
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:24,800
Only the heart-blood of a beloved one
can break the curse.

137
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:29,519
Now that your Butterfly Seal is fading,

138
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,879
looks like Your Highness

139
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,200
is deeply in love with me.

140
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,240
You were nothing but a tool

141
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:41,000
to break the curse

142
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,039
and preserve my life.

143
00:08:44,279 --> 00:08:45,480
What you call affection

144
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,879
was merely pity, nothing more.

145
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:53,559
A lowly wretch,
with his entire family slaughtered,

146
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:56,240
set up just a few little schemes

147
00:08:57,679 --> 00:08:59,679
to bring the once-lofty princess

148
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:01,679
to such depths.

149
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:04,080
I heard that your father

150
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:06,440
was also of lowly birth.

151
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:10,200
To your mother, your beloved father

152
00:09:10,879 --> 00:09:14,320
was nothing but a disposable tool.

153
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:17,240
Don't you dare insult my father!

154
00:09:20,039 --> 00:09:21,399
You deserve this curse!

155
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:23,799
Consumed by suffering,

156
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:27,639
never to rise again.

157
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,679
Cold, isn't it?

158
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,240
Tell me where the Mu's royal seal is,

159
00:09:41,039 --> 00:09:42,120
and I will allow you

160
00:09:43,159 --> 00:09:45,399
to warm yourself by the fire.

161
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,360
You won't talk?

162
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,320
It's alright.

163
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:57,919
Let me warm you up.

164
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,080
Ling Xiao!

165
00:10:13,759 --> 00:10:15,799
You won't get a word from me!

166
00:10:16,879 --> 00:10:19,080
You will never get the royal seal!

167
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,440
Then don't blame me for being ruthless.

168
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,360
What do you want now?

169
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:29,600
You beast!

170
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,399
Come at me instead!

171
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,279
Without the royal seal,

172
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:36,159
how could Xiling's crown change hands?

173
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:40,559
And how can I ascend the throne?

174
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:43,799
No!

175
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:45,919
No!

176
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,039
Mother!

177
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:51,879
Mother!

178
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:53,840
Ling Xiao!

179
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,559
You took over our place,

180
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:58,279
yet you still dream of
becoming the King of Xiling.

181
00:10:58,559 --> 00:11:00,639
You know what I want.

182
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,480
A new king,

183
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,480
or a fallen kingdom,

184
00:11:06,759 --> 00:11:08,799
the choice is yours.

185
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:16,159
I wish for death

186
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:20,039
to apologize to your father

187
00:11:20,679 --> 00:11:21,759
and stay with him.

188
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,720
Mother, no!

189
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,320
No!

190
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:27,039
Mother!

191
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,600
Mother!

192
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:35,919
Ling Xiao,

193
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:39,279
if you spare my mother's life,

194
00:11:41,639 --> 00:11:42,759
I will tell you

195
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,519
where the royal seal is.
